## defaultRenderOption() function

> This API is provided as an alpha preview for developers and may change based on feedback that we receive. Do not use this API in a production environment.
> 

Default function for rendering the options in the `CountryCodeSelector`<!-- -->'s `Autocomplete` component. See [https://mui.com/material-ui/api/autocomplete/\#autocomplete-prop-renderOption](https://mui.com/material-ui/api/autocomplete/#autocomplete-prop-renderOption) for more information about the `renderOption` prop.

**Signature:**

```typescript
export declare function defaultRenderOption(props: React.HTMLAttributes<HTMLLIElement>, option: CountryType): React.ReactNode;
```
